Kapp拍攝的](http://bn.banglapedia.org/index.php?title=%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A5%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%95_%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%B2)[Northbrook
Hall](http://bn.banglapedia.org/index.php?title=%E0%A6%A8%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%A5%E0%A6%AC%E0%A7%8D%E0%A6%B0%E0%A7%81%E0%A6%95_%E0%A6%B9%E0%A6%B2)[(Lal
